      <li><strong>5-tray / 5 kg blast chiller (entry-level)</strong>: ₹1,50,000 – ₹2,20,000</li>
      <li><strong>10-tray / 10 kg blast chiller</strong>: ₹2,20,000 – ₹3,50,000</li>
      <li><strong>20-tray / 20 kg blast chiller</strong>: ₹3,50,000 – ₹5,00,000</li>
      <li><strong>40-tray / 40 kg blast chiller/freezer</strong>: ₹5,00,000 – ₹8,00,000</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Key brands: Irinox (Italy) is the gold standard for blast chillers. Electrolux Professional, Coldline, and Friginox are other well-regarded brands. Some Indian commercial refrigeration companies have introduced entry-level blast chillers, but quality varies significantly.</p>

